short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays Snek Rank On Listings On DigitalEyes/Solanart

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Display next to snek name the rank of the snek from the unofficial Howrare ranking while you're browsing Solanart or Digital Eyes.

Version 2.0: 
- Added support for pesky penguins on Magic Eden and Digital Eyes


Solanart: https://solanart.io/collections/thesneks

DE: https://digitaleyes.market/collections/The%20Sneks

Push notifications via Discord DM's for when floors or prices changes on certain sneks is coming soon.
